<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.5">
<l>ivaḷaip peṟumpari civvaṇaṅ kāṭuta laṉṟantō</l>
<l>kuvaḷait taṭaṅkaṇṇuṅ kōvaic cevvāyum payantaṉaḷ</l>
<l>kavaḷak kaṭākkaḷi ṟaṭṭa pirāṉṟiru nāmattā</l>
<l>ṟavaḷap poṭikkoṇṭu nīriṭ ṭiṭumiṉ ṟaṇiyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The way of getting her [back] is not this dancing as demonesses, alas.</l>
<l>She has become pale to [her] broad lotus eyes and her Kōvai-red mouth.</l>
<l>Put water with white powder, along with the auspicious name</l>
<l>of the lord who killed the elephant in rut by [its] tusk. She will calm down.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
